      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nAll settled monetary transactions from FIS STDMON Data XTRACT v3.8. Includes value loads, purchases, reversals, and adjustments. Click any tile to jump to the transaction detail table.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Txn Type Code | `fact_monetary.txn_type_code` | 1710=Value Load \u00b7 5=Purchase \u00b7 1=Reversal \u00b7 1720=Adjustment |\n| Settle Amount | `fact_monetary.settle_amount` | Dollar amount of settled transaction |\n| Purse Code | `fact_monetary.purse_code` | OTC2100 \u00b7 FOD2100 \u00b7 CMB2100 |\n| Response Code | `fact_monetary.response_code` | 0=Completed OK \u00b7 other=error |\n| Work of Date | `fact_monetary.work_of_date` | FIS reporting date |\n| Pan Proxy | `fact_monetary.pan_proxy_number` | Card proxy (links to `dim_member.fis_person_id`) |\n\n> Current data contains **498 value loads** ($114,540) across 166 members \u00d7 3 purses. Purchase and reversal transactions will appear here once members start using cards.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
